{"code":0,"data":[{"cid":595278,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":123626,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"技术上应该是可以的，可是你就算知道是谁截出去的又能怎么办呢？","timestamp":1605964474,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":595284,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":123626,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Alice: 封他号啊，永封并禁止浏览。","timestamp":1605964531,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":595285,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":123626,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"可以加，但是没用。只需要截图不带背景就行了。","timestamp":1605964544,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":595297,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":123626,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Alice: 如果是恶意截图带节奏，造成糟糕影响，或者造成有人被网络暴力等等后果，就该封号。\n当然如果无伤大雅那应该还行……也不至于这么狠_(:з」∠)_","timestamp":1605964639,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":595300,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":123626,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re 洞主: 如果我知道这个设定，我可以用别的手机来拍屏幕呀，这样不管什么后台技术手段也锁定不到截图者本人了","timestamp":1605964674,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":595301,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":123626,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"感觉技术上是可行的。","timestamp":1605964677,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":595313,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{"h":1748,"w":806},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":123626,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Bob: 截图不可能不带背景……我是这个意思。随便草图示意了一下……加在对话框上。","timestamp":1605964806,"type":"image","url":"5e/5euezesg4w34bb3ufwxmg7isewkuypal.jpeg"},{"cid":595317,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":123626,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Alice: 这倒也是，但至少可以震慑一部分人_(:з」∠)_","timestamp":1605964898,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":595335,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":123626,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"先不说一部分水印不能反推到用户id，而且我再手机拍个照更没了。","timestamp":1605965086,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":595351,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":123626,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Dave: 不一定是一部分？突然在想，或许可以整个页面加一个透明的水印层，不可操作，不影响点击下面的东西，不随滚轮滚动。","timestamp":1605965223,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":595357,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Eve","permissions":["report"],"pid":123626,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"据我所知一些办公软件是有这个的。每个人屏幕上会显示id，不过很浅很不明显，但是加个滤镜一下就能看出来。有人上传公司内部消息到互联网上就被公司通过这个查水表了。","timestamp":1605965255,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":595363,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":123626,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Dave: 拍照这个确实无解。只能说，至少有一部分人可能并不想这么麻烦……而且拍照会暴露硬件信息。","timestamp":1605965299,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":595369,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Eve","permissions":["report"],"pid":123626,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"当然这么搞的话，树洞其实就不匿名了（","timestamp":1605965409,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":595412,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":123626,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"而且有些截图是无伤大雅的，比如截个树洞段子发给朋友甚至发微博，无带节奏的主观恶意且内容也没问题的，我认为应该允许。\n如果技术可能的话，要是只有通过管理员知道的算法才能解码水印那就太好了。（因为如果允许无伤大雅的发截图又在截图上加水印，如果是太容易解码的方法，似乎也迷之危险，外面的世界好危险。）","timestamp":1605965784,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":595496,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":123626,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re 洞主: 你说的这些技术上应该都是可以实现的","timestamp":1605966583,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":595626,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Francis","permissions":["report"],"pid":123626,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"OCR出来文本什么水印都没了（","timestamp":1605967982,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":595682,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":123626,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Francis: 这个不担心……文本复制也可以呀。但若不是截图，就不能证明真实性。张口就来谁不会2333 负面影响就小多了。","timestamp":1605968603,"type":"text","url":""}],"post":{"attention":false,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"likenum":3,"permissions":["report","fold"],"pid":123626,"reply":17,"tag":null,"text":"不知道原理上可不可行——\n能不能在树洞加肉眼不可见的水印啊，比如每一个洞主和评论的灰色背景上面，不知道能不能加肉眼不可见，但可以被计算机解析的水印。\n而且能不能每个人水印不一样，比如就是本人哈希值？\n#试图避免有人把树洞截出去\n#不懂计算机\n#不行就算了","timestamp":1605964338,"type":"text","updated_at":1606782652,"url":"","vote":{}}}